-- ============================================================
-- Hungry Dead (Ravenous Dead Redesign): alonecraft_spell_dbc overrides
-- ============================================================
-- Redesign: "Your ghouls deal X% more damage for each of your diseases on the target."
-- Rank 1 (48965): 4% per disease (BasePoints=3, displayed as BP+1=4)
-- Rank 2 (49571): 7% per disease (BasePoints=6, displayed as BP+1=7)
-- Rank 3 (49572): 10% per disease (BasePoints=9, displayed as BP+1=10)
--
-- Effect1 changed to SPELL_AURA_DUMMY holding the percentage value.
-- Effect2/Effect3 zeroed out (removes old Strength/ghoul contribution bonuses).
-- Actual damage logic is in C++ UnitScript (HungryDead.cpp).

-- Hungry Dead Rank 1 (was Ravenous Dead)
